Ing '''Pala''' (a misusulat muring '''Palai''' ([[Malayalam]] : പാലാ), metung yang balen king dakeng matalimunduk king aslagan ning [[Kottayam (distritu)]] king [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] ning [[Kerala]]. Atiu king pampangan ning [[Meenachil River|Ilug Meenachil]], at pun tanggapan (''headquarters'') ne ning [[Meenachil]] Taluk ampo ning Pala Revenue Division. Iti ing manimunang pasbul dalan (''gateway'') papunta kareng mangatas a kabundukan ning mauli (''southern high ranges'').

